paths: Obvious exits: north, east, west, out
description: Several glass display cases with miniature room models line the walls of this tidy shop.  Decorated with lilliputian furniture, each tiny room shows how well Whimbly's wall treatments compliment the homeowner's styles.  The proprietor wrings her hands expectantly as she watches you browse.
